ectrum of PAHs and VSGs in favor of large PAHs while B stars destroy even the\nlargest PAHs up to large radii in the disk. These results allow us to put new\nconstrains on the properties of two sources: IRS 48 and \"Gomez's Hamburger\"\nwhich are poorly characterized.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Nov 2008 16:44:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Jan 2009 15:55:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
